Hundreds of pages of sworn depositions, emails, and reports from companies including Deloitte, Pitcher Partners, and Charter Keck Cramer are flooding lawyers including Allan Myers, QC, and advocates for both sides.
Mrs De Lutis and her late husband Luigi were Italian immigrants who ran milk bars and delicacies since the 1950s and bought a shop in Brunswick in the 1970s.
